  "keyFeatures": [
    "Game engine-independent C++ core library",
    "Entity-based network model (Pole, Port, Span, Bundle)",
    "Automatic connection generation from path specifications",
    "Incremental dirty tracking and recalculation",
    "Port slot template system with automatic layout",
    "Support for corner angle correction and multi-conductor bundles",
    "Lightweight viewer for development and debugging",
    "Validation system for topology and connection integrity"
